      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja manna Sirds pee kab-\nas Seewas irr likkusi peelabbi-\natees/ jeb efinu es pee fawa\nTuwaka Durwin gluhnejs/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad (lai noteek/) ka\nnanna Seewa no Zitta tohp\npfnieta/ un ka weens Swe-\nchajs pee tahs gull.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo fchi irr weena negan-\na Leeta/ un irr weens Nosee-\numis preefsch teem Teetas-Kun-\ngeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas buhtu tahds Ug-\nuns/ tas lihds paschai Samai-\naschanai rihj/ un wiſſu mannu\nBadohmu buhtu isfaknojs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Efinu es manna Kalpa\neb mannas Kalpones Teefu niz-\ntnajs/ kad teem prett manni\nas bija?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ko warretu es darriht/\nad tas STIPRAJS\nDEES zeltohs? uu kad\nwiſſch peemeekletu/ ko warretu es\ntbildeht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Neggi tas/ kas manni\nekfch Mahtes Mecfahin darrija/\nvinuu arri irr darrijs? un tas\nats irr muhs Meeſâs fataifijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Efinu es taim Rabbagam\needsis/ kas tam gribbejahs/ jeb\nahs Atraitnes Azziſ lizzis no-\nginst?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Efinu es fawn Rummo-\nn weenspats ehdihs/ ta ka tas\nBahrixch arridsan ne buhtu no\na ehdis?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo no mannas Jaunibas\nwiſſch pee mannim usau-\nsis/ itt ka pee Tehwa/ un no\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "manna Mahtes Mecfahm efinu\nes wiſſu eepreezinajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Efinu es kahdu redsejs\nbohjâ eetam/ ka taim Drehbju\nne bija/ un ka taim Behdigam\nApfegga ne bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja wiſſa Gurnf man\nne buhtu pateikufchi/ kad wiſſch\nno mannu Jehru Ahdahin fa-\nkillahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Efinu es fatwu Rohku\nprett to Bahrixu pazehlis/ ta-\npehz ka es eeftch * Wahrtim re-\ndfeju man ko eespehjam.\n* Tas irr, Eekfch Teefas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad lai mans Kamme-\nsts no to Plezzu Rauleem atkrit/\nun manna Rohka lai noluhft no\nfawahin Dilbahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta STIPRA DEG-\nWA Samaitaschanu es pahr\nmannim bihjajohs/ un ne war-\nreju to darriht preefsch wiſſa\nAugstibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Efinu es to Sestu par\nmannu Zerribu lizzis? jeb us to\nfchihstu Sestu fazzijs: Mans\nPatwerums?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Efinu es preezajees pahr\nto/ ka man leela Manta bija/\nun ka manna Rohka tohti daudf\nbij jainantojsi?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Efinu es to Gaifchunu\nusluhkojs/ kad tas iposch bija/\njeb to Mehnefi/ kad tas gaifchi\ntezczeja?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Irr manna Sirds likku-\ntees peelabbinates fleppent/ ka\nmanna Rohka mannu Matti\nbuhtu fkahpstijsi?\n"
    }
  ],
